<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Edit view</strong> (<span class="icon "><i class="psicon-design_inline_edit"></i></span>)</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Opens the dashboard for editing.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Undo</strong> (<span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-reply  "></i></span>)</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Undoes the last change, unless this change has already been saved.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Redo</strong> (<span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-share  "></i></span>)</p></td>
