<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">This area displays the dashboard view that is currently opened. Click on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-sort-down  "></i></span> to switch to another view or to <a href="#407">create a new view</a>.</p></td>
</tr>
