<p>In addition, there are a few useful additional functions available for graphs, regardless of the type. For example, you can download graphs as images or easily access the data displayed in the graph directly from the dashboard. Refer to the chapter <a href="#750">Using additional functions for graphs</a> for more information.</p>
</div>
